Florida
So much of the order of February 3, 1913, creating Phosphate Reserve No. 16, Florida No. 5, as affects the lands hereinafter described is hereby revoked, and all such lands not otherwise reserved or withdrawn are hereby restored to the public domain and to disposition under the laws applicable thereto.
TALLAHASSEE MERIDIAN
T. 33 S., R. 27 E., sec. 7, NW. ¼ of NE. ¼, NE. ¼ of SE. ¼;
sec. 15, SE. ¼ of SE. ¼;
sec. 20, NW. ¼ of NE.¼, NE. ¼ of NW. ¼;
sec. 30, W. ½ of NE. ¼.
HERBERT HOOVER
The White House,
May 23, 1930.
